    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior shows extensive wear, including noticeable dents, fading paint, and some areas of surface rust. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears and stains, and some interior trim pieces are missing or damaged. Mechanically, the car starts but runs roughly, and it likely needs major engine or transmission repairs, along with a full suspension overhaul. This is an ideal candidate for a dedicated project car or a source for parts, but it is not currently suitable for daily use.",
