      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready for a new home and many more miles of adventures. It looks great and runs even better\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
